<item>
            <title>[SYNAPSE-512] If a message is sent to a proxy service is GET and if the outputType is SOAP Synapse sends a GET instead of a POST</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SYNAPSE-512</link>
                <project id="12310201" key="SYNAPSE">Synapse</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;&amp;lt;syn:proxy name=&quot;StockQuoteProxy&quot; transports=&quot;https http&quot; startOnLoad=&quot;true&quot; statistics=&quot;disable&quot; trace=&quot;disable&quot;&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
        &amp;lt;syn:target&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
            &amp;lt;syn:inSequence&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
                &amp;lt;syn:log level=&quot;full&quot;/&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
                &amp;lt;syn:send&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
                    &amp;lt;syn:endpoint&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
                        &amp;lt;syn:address uri=&quot;http://localhost:9001/services/SimpleStockQuoteService&quot; format=&quot;soap11&quot;/&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
                    &amp;lt;/syn:endpoint&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
                &amp;lt;/syn:send&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
            &amp;lt;/syn:inSequence&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
            &amp;lt;syn:outSequence&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
                &amp;lt;syn:send/&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
            &amp;lt;/syn:outSequence&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
        &amp;lt;/syn:target&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
        &amp;lt;syn:publishWSDL uri=&quot;http://localhost:9000/services/SimpleStockQuoteService?wsdl&quot;/&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
    &amp;lt;/syn:proxy&amp;gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;If a message is sent to the above Proxy Service Synapse sends a GET instead of a SOAP message over POST. This works if the following Axis2 property is set though&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&amp;lt;syn:proxy name=&quot;StockQuoteProxy&quot; transports=&quot;https http&quot; startOnLoad=&quot;true&quot; statistics=&quot;disable&quot; trace=&quot;disable&quot;&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
        &amp;lt;syn:target&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
            &amp;lt;syn:inSequence&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
                &amp;lt;syn:log level=&quot;full&quot;/&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
                &amp;lt;syn:property name=&quot;HTTP_METHOD&quot; value=&quot;POST&quot; scope=&quot;axis2&quot;/&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
                &amp;lt;syn:send&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
                    &amp;lt;syn:endpoint&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
                        &amp;lt;syn:address uri=&quot;http://localhost:9001/services/SimpleStockQuoteService&quot; format=&quot;soap11&quot;/&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
                    &amp;lt;/syn:endpoint&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
                &amp;lt;/syn:send&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
            &amp;lt;/syn:inSequence&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
            &amp;lt;syn:outSequence&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
                &amp;lt;syn:send/&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
            &amp;lt;/syn:outSequence&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
        &amp;lt;/syn:target&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
        &amp;lt;syn:publishWSDL uri=&quot;http://localhost:9000/services/SimpleStockQuoteService?wsdl&quot;/&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
    &amp;lt;/syn:proxy&amp;gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
